    "description": "Ninjacart Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Frontend Developer for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Ninjacart Digital Technologies:\nNinjacart Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ninjacart Digital Technologies!",
